# demo-app (v2.0.0)

## Routes
- POST /users — Creates a new user
- GET /users

## Tools
- createUser — Creates a new user

See /openapi.json for the full API schema and /mcp for the MCP endpoint.
All errors are application/problem+json (RFC 9457).

